content: 감사합니다! 더 도움이 되길 바랍니다. 제가 도와줄 수 있는 게 있다면 언제든지 물어봐 주세요.화이팅!
Hello! My day is going well, thank you. How can I assist you today?
Don't give me any suggestion about a job interview.
Understood! How can I assist you today?
I have an interview for Google back-end development. Can you give me any suggestion?

Sure! Make sure to showcase your problem-solving skills, knowledge of data structures and algorithms, and experience with back-end technologies. Practice coding on whiteboard and be prepared to answer technical questions confidently. Good luck!
